{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Jess2.xyz","author":"Jess2","siteUrl":"http://jess2.xyz","comment":{"disqusShortName":"https-jess2-netlify-com","utterances":""},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"Jess2"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"67f13185-5163-5a15-9842-8ca6e03d38d0","excerpt":"CSS 만으로 서서히 나타나고 서서히 사라지는 애니메이션을 구현할 수 있다. 우선, 애니메이션 속성에 대해 알아보자. Animation Animation 속성은 애니메이션에 이름을 지정하거나 지속시간, 속도 조절 등을 지정할 수 있는 속성을 가지고 있다. 애니메이션 속성 종류  : @keyframes 이름 (예제에서는 fadeOut 을 사용)  : 타임 프레임의 길이, 키프레임이 동작하는 시간을 설정할 때 사용  : 애니메이션 속도 조절 / 그래프 ( linear / ease / ease-in…","html":"<p><span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 741px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 47.7726574500768%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"css\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/a57cee6fedec9eb2dcb707f33708f676/111a3/css.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a57cee6fedec9eb2dcb707f33708f676/94807/css.png 185w,\n/static/a57cee6fedec9eb2dcb707f33708f676/db9f8/css.png 371w,\n/static/a57cee6fedec9eb2dcb707f33708f676/111a3/css.png 741w,\n/static/a57cee6fedec9eb2dcb707f33708f676/248f3/css.png 1112w,\n/static/a57cee6fedec9eb2dcb707f33708f676/ffc6e/css.png 1302w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 741px) 100vw, 741px\"\n      />\n  </span></p>\n<p>CSS 만으로 서서히 나타나고 서서히 사라지는 애니메이션을 구현할 수 있다.</p>\n<p>우선, 애니메이션 속성에 대해 알아보자.</p>\n<h3 id=\"animation\"><a href=\"#animation\" aria-label=\"animation permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Animation</h3>\n<p>Animation 속성은 애니메이션에 이름을 지정하거나 지속시간, 속도 조절 등을 지정할 수 있는 속성을 가지고 있다.</p>\n<h4 id=\"애니메이션-속성-종류\"><a href=\"#%EC%95%A0%EB%8B%88%EB%A9%94%EC%9D%B4%EC%85%98-%EC%86%8D%EC%84%B1-%EC%A2%85%EB%A5%98\" aria-label=\"애니메이션 속성 종류 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>애니메이션 속성 종류</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">animation-name</code> : @keyframes 이름 (예제에서는 fadeOut 을 사용)</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">animation-duratuion</code> : 타임 프레임의 길이, 키프레임이 동작하는 시간을 설정할 때 사용</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">animation-timing-function</code> : 애니메이션 속도 조절 / 그래프 ( linear / ease / ease-in / ease-out / ease-in-out / cubic-bezier )</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">animation-delay</code> : 애니메이션을 시작하기 전 지연시간 설정</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">animation-iteration-count</code> : 반복 횟수 지정</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">animation-direction</code> : 반복 방향 설정 ( 정방향 / 역방향 / 번갈아가며)</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">animation-fill-mode</code> : 애니메이션 시작 / 끝 상태 제어 ( none / forwords / backwords / both )</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"fade-in\"><a href=\"#fade-in\" aria-label=\"fade in permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Fade In</h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">opacity</code>를 애니메이션으로 n초 동안 0에서 1까지 주면 된다. (from: 0, to: 1)</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.fade-in-box</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> inline-block<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> yellow<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 10px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">animation</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> fadein 3s<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">-moz-animation</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> fadein 3s<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* Firefox */</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">-webkit-animation</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> fadein 3s<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* Safari and Chrome */</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">-o-animation</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> fadein 3s<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* Opera */</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@keyframes</span> fadein</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token selector\">from</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\">opacity</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token selector\">to</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\">opacity</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@-moz-keyframes</span> fadein</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* Firefox */</span>\n    <span class=\"token selector\">from</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\">opacity</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token selector\">to</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\">opacity</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@-webkit-keyframes</span> fadein</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* Safari and Chrome */</span>\n    <span class=\"token selector\">from</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\">opacity</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token selector\">to</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\">opacity</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@-o-keyframes</span> fadein</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* Opera */</span>\n    <span class=\"token selector\">from</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\">opacity</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token selector\">to</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\">opacity</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"fade-in-실행-결과\"><a href=\"#fade-in-%EC%8B%A4%ED%96%89-%EA%B2%B0%EA%B3%BC\" aria-label=\"fade in 실행 결과 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Fade In 실행 결과</h3>\n<iframe height=\"265\" style=\"width: 100%;\" scrolling=\"no\" title=\"Fade In\" src=\"https://codepen.io/je_ss2/embed/zYvPNLj?height=265&theme-id=dark&default-tab=result\" frameborder=\"no\" allowtransparency=\"true\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  See the Pen <a href='https://codepen.io/je_ss2/pen/zYvPNLj'>Fade In</a> by SoyeonJung\n  (<a href='https://codepen.io/je_ss2'>@je_ss2</a>) on <a href='https://codepen.io'>CodePen</a>.\n</iframe>\n<ul>\n<li>우측 하단의 ‘Rerun’ 버튼을 누르면 실행 결과를 다시 볼 수 있다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"fade-out\"><a href=\"#fade-out\" aria-label=\"fade out permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Fade Out</h3>\n<p>Fade In과 반대로 <code class=\"language-text\">opacity</code>를 애니메이션으로 n초 동안 1에서 0까지 주면 된다. (from: 1, to: 0)</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.fade-out-box</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> inline-block<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> yellow<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 10px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">animation</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> fadeout 3s<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">-moz-animation</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> fadeout 3s<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* Firefox */</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">-webkit-animation</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> fadeout 3s<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* Safari and Chrome */</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">-o-animation</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> fadeout 3s<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* Opera */</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">animation-fill-mode</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> forwards<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@keyframes</span> fadeout</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token selector\">from</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\">opacity</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token selector\">to</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\">opacity</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@-moz-keyframes</span> fadeout</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* Firefox */</span>\n    <span class=\"token selector\">from</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\">opacity</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token selector\">to</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\">opacity</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@-webkit-keyframes</span> fadeout</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* Safari and Chrome */</span>\n    <span class=\"token selector\">from</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\">opacity</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token selector\">to</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\">opacity</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@-o-keyframes</span> fadeout</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* Opera */</span>\n    <span class=\"token selector\">from</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\">opacity</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token selector\">to</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\">opacity</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"fade-out-실행-결과\"><a href=\"#fade-out-%EC%8B%A4%ED%96%89-%EA%B2%B0%EA%B3%BC\" aria-label=\"fade out 실행 결과 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Fade Out 실행 결과</h3>\n<iframe height=\"265\" style=\"width: 100%;\" scrolling=\"no\" title=\"Fade Out\" src=\"https://codepen.io/je_ss2/embed/bGVYgPB?height=265&theme-id=dark&default-tab=result\" frameborder=\"no\" allowtransparency=\"true\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  See the Pen <a href='https://codepen.io/je_ss2/pen/bGVYgPB'>Fade Out</a> by SoyeonJung\n  (<a href='https://codepen.io/je_ss2'>@je_ss2</a>) on <a href='https://codepen.io'>CodePen</a>.\n</iframe>\n<ul>\n<li>우측 하단의 ‘Rerun’ 버튼을 누르면 실행 결과를 다시 볼 수 있다.</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"[CSS] Fade In / Fade Out Animation 추가하기","date":"May 03, 2020"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/css/fade-in-out/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/JavaScript/ecmascript-2020/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[JavaScript] ECMAScript2020 소개 및 주요 개념","category":"javascript"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/web/storage/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[web] Cookie vs LocalStorage vs SessionStorage","category":"web"}}}}